<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weebsite/styles/variables.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weebsite/styles/indexstyles.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weebsite/styles/community.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weebsite/styles/post.css" />

  <script src="/weebsite/scripts/include.js" defer></script>
  <script src="/weebsite/scripts/button.js" defer></script>
  <title></title>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="layout-container"></div>

  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="community-header">
      <!-- COMMUNITY BANNER-->
      <div class="community-metadata">
        <div class="community-description">
          Interspecies Reviewers is a Japanese fantasy comedy manga series
          written by Amahara and illustrated by masha. It has been serialized
          through Nico Nico Seiga's manga website Dragon Dragon Age since August
          2016 and has been collected in ten tankobon volumes by Fujimi Shobo.
        </div>
        <div class="community-stat">
          <div class="stat">
            <p class="stat-value">18k</p>
            <p class="stat-name">Members</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <p class="stat-value">69</p>
            <p class="stat-name">Online</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <p class="stat-value">Jun 28, 2019</p>
            <p class="stat-name">Created</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="follow-com-button">Follow</button>
      </div>
      <!-- COMMUNITY BANNER-->
      <div class="communityBanner">
        <img src="images/animepic1.png" class="communityBannerImage" />
        <div class="communityBannerText">
          <div class="communityTitle">w/interspeciesReviewers</div>
        </div>
        <img
          src="images/interspeciesReviewers.png"
          class="communityHeaderImage"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="post">
      <!-- Post Content -->
      <div class="postContent">
        <!-- Post Header -->
        <div class="postHeader">
          <!-- Left Side: User Info -->
          <div class="postHeaderLeft">
            <span
              class="actionButton"
              onclick="window.open('community.html', '_self')"
            >
              <img src="images/interspeciesReviewers.png" class="pfp" alt="" />
              <span class="postUsername">w/interspeciesReviewers /</span>
            </span>
            <span
              class="actionButton"
              onclick="window.open('profile.html', '_self')"
            >
              <img src="images/pfp.png" class="pfp" alt="" />
              <span class="postUsername">u/ishigamiYu</span>
            </span>
            <span class="postTime"> 2 hours ago</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Right Side: Kebab Menu Icon -->
        </div>

        <!-- Post Title -->
        <h2 class="postTitle" onclick="window.open('postView.html', '_self')">
          [Interspecies Reviewers] Should I watch Interspecies Reviewers?
        </h2>

        <!-- Post Body -->
        <div class="postBody" onclick="window.open('postView.html', '_self')">
          <p>
            My friend kept telling me about this show in school going all like
            "oh should watch it and then review it so that you get a double
            review" And it does look interesting, it has an interesting premise,
            but at the same time I heard that there's a lot of
            not-so-kid-friendly content within the show (yes you know what I'm
            talking about). Normally I don't watch a movie or TV show if THAT is
            front and center, but I have heard some good things about this anime
            and I'm willing to try it out, but I definitely would be
            uncomfortable if the only reason to watch it is for those scenes.
            Should I give it a go? Why do you think so?
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Post Actions -->
        <div class="postActions">
          <div class="reactionsContainer">
            <!-- Thumbs Up Box -->
            <div class="reactionBox">
              <button class="actionButton like-button" aria-label="Thumbs Up">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path
                    d="M1 21h4V9H1v12z M23 10c0-1.1-0.9-2-2-2h-6.31l0.95-4.57a1.983 1.983 0 0 0-0.44-1.74L14.17 1l-6.58 6.59A2 2 0 0 0 7 9v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h9c0.83 0 1.54-0.5 1.84-1.22l3.02-7.05c0.09-0.23 0.14-0.47 0.14-0.73v-2z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </button>
              <span class="voteCount">426,960</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Thumbs Down Box -->
            <div class="reactionBox">
              <button
                class="actionButton dislike-button"
                aria-label="Thumbs Down"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path
                    d="M23 3h-4v12h4V3z M1 14c0 1.1 0.9 2 2 2h6.31l-0.95 4.57a1.983 1.983 0 0 0 0.44 1.74L9.83 23l6.58-6.59c0.36-0.36 0.58-0.86 0.58-1.41V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5c-0.83 0-1.54 0.5-1.84 1.22L0.14 11.27c-0.09 0.23-0.14 0.47-0.14 0.73v2z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </button>
              <span class="voteCount">6,960</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Comment Box -->
            <div class="reactionBox">
              <button
                class="actionButton"
                aria-label="Comment"
                onclick="window.open('postView.html', '_self')"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 16 16"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="size-4"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M8 2C4.262 2 1 4.57 1 8c0 1.86.98 3.486 2.455 4.566a3.472 3.472 0 0 1-.469 1.26.75.75 0 0 0 .713 1.14 6.961 6.961 0 0 0 3.06-1.06c.403.062.818.094 1.241.094 3.738 0 7-2.57 7-6s-3.262-6-7-6ZM5 9a1 1 0 1 0 0-2 1 1 0 0 0 0 2Zm7-1a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0ZM8 9a1 1 0 1 0 0-2 1 1 0 0 0 0 2Z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"
                  />
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Share Box -->
            <div class="reactionBox">
              <button class="actionButton" aria-label="Share">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 16 16"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="size-4"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M12 6a2 2 0 1 0-1.994-1.842L5.323 6.5a2 2 0 1 0 0 3l4.683 2.342a2 2 0 1 0 .67-1.342L5.995 8.158a2.03 2.03 0 0 0 0-.316L10.677 5.5c.353.311.816.5 1.323.5Z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- End of Post Content -->
    </div>
  </div>
</body>